transcript:
[Ringing]
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan ji boliye.
Customer: Ji namaskar sir Siddhant bol raha hun.
Executive: Bolo.
Customer: Sir kal call kiya tha aapne?
Executive: Nahi maine call nahi kiya.
Executive: Kal ya parso mein aapne call kiya sham ko 6 baje kareeb aapka ticket aaya sir.
Customer: Wo ticket ka message to mere ko bhi aaya lekin maine call kiya nahi.
Executive: Aapne nahi kiya ye 944 last mein isi number se call aaya tha sir. 5 bajke 42 minute pe.
Customer: Sir aapka call aaya hoga aur nahi utha hoga to maine samne call kiya hoga baki kuch nahi hai.
Executive: Achcha okay okay to ticket load kar do sir main ye?
Customer: Haan band kar do.
Executive: Okay sir okay.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer received a ticket message but did not make the call.



Resolution:

- Executive will close the ticket.



Next Steps: 

Issue resolved



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

ticket, call
